- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the implementation of a workload management system for a Grid computing infrastructure. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the development and update of a software system. 
- cs.Distributed Systems is another possible category as the paper deals with the management of distributed resources. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of the workload management system for scientific applications. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on programming languages, but rather on the architecture and functionality of the workload management system.
